issue.title: finished converting post request to string with audio contents
issue.body:
# Summary

Modified post endpoint to accept encoded byte string. This will later be decoded and saved into a `.wav` file for it to be passed to the google `speech_recognition` library.

/cc @syedrokib @cabrer32 @ander601 @ander710

issue.title: removing routes from challenge project
issue.body:
# Summary 

Refactored project, removing old code from Shopify Challenge. Removed every endpoint except for the POST: `/translator` .

# To Test
- checkout to this branch `cleaning_up_project` . 
- `docker-compose down`
-  `docker-compose up --build -d`
- Test that POST `/translator`, make sure it works as expected.

/cc @syedrokib @ander601 @ander710
